    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
