    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is prioritized with a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Equipped with cross-drilled rotors for optimal heat dissipation and staggered Style 67 alloys, this M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience with the mechanical sortedness required for spirited use.",
