    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the driver-side rear quarter panel\u2014typical signs of careful road use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no major curbing. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment with premium upholstery that remains taut and comfortable, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection performed just last month. The brakes feel firm, the transmission shifts smoothly, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle perfect for someone who values a documented maintenance history and an honest presentation.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
