      "description": "This expertly curated vehicle represents a sophisticated acquisition for the discerning motorist. It exhibits commendable mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, reflecting a history of diligent maintenance and responsible ownership. Rigorously evaluated to ensure it meets our established standards for reliability and performance, this model offers a refined driving experience and exceptional long-term value. Secure a vehicle that exemplifies both engineering excellence and professional care.",
      "price": 34900.0,
