    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. The interior is nice and clean, and it runs like a dream! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable, stylish car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
