    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Silver Grey Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle is mechanically robust, featuring documented VANOS servicing and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The chassis remains composed with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension components. While the car exhibits honest patina consistent with spirited use, the Laguna Seca Blue interior remains a functional and supportive cockpit. This is a well-maintained, turn-key performance icon optimized for the driving purist.",
